<br />
Before including the file &quot;includes/functions_bbas.php&quot;, define a function named &quot;bbas_filter_contacts&quot;. This function gets an array of the links as the parameter. This function should return an array, which is the new list of the links.
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">and how to allow posting with the DNS name of my site? it is blocking right now...</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
Next version of bbAntiSpam will support posting links to the site where the forum is located. But now you have to write code in &quot;bbas_filter_contacts&quot;.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
